VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \[RoutePrefix\("
WHEN EXPR MISSING:Authorize|RequireAuthorization|ApiKeyRequired|[ApiController] && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of [RoutePrefix] attribute in an API controller, potentially indicating improper route prefix configuration.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for API Route Prefix: Improper Usage.
